{"word":"H4801 - מֶרְחָק - merchâq - mer-khawk' - Far - தூரம்","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>מֶרְחָק"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>merchâq"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>mer-khawk'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Far / தூரம்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"தூரம், கடையாந்தரம் - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"distant place, distance, far country"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/H7368 - רָחַק - râchaq - raw-khak'/7368\">H7368</a>; <i>remoteness</i>, that is, (concretely) a <i>distant</i> place; often (adverbially) <i>from afar</i>: -  (a, dwell in, very) far (country, off). See also <a href=\"#/H1023 - בֵּית הַמֶּרְחָק - Bêyth ham-Merchâq - bayth ham-mer-khawk'/1023\">H1023</a>."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4801 - מֶרְחָק - merchâq - mer-khawk'/4801\">H4801</a>, <a href=\"#/H7350 - רָחֹוק - râchôwq - raw-khoke'/7350\">H7350</a>, <a href=\"#/H7368 - רָחַק - râchaq - raw-khak'/7368\">H7368</a>, <a href=\"#/H7369 - רָחֵק - râchêq - raw-khake'/7369\">H7369</a>"}]}